	(80, 1, '2015-11-26 22:28:55', '2015-11-26 22:28:55', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="25px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="7/12"][vc_custom_heading text="WELCOME TO BLUNOVA DOG SHOW!" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:center|color:%23444444" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">Our Company was born from our Passion for all things Dog Show!</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">We specialize mainly in Dog Show Products and making personalized accessories for All Breeds of Dogs, their Kennels, their Handlers and their loving Owners &amp; Families. However, our products are not limited to Show people, we also cater to any Dog Lover out there who just loves their Pet or is a fan of their Breed.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">Our Company launched in 2014 exclusively producing Australian Shepherd items, but we quickly started getting requests for more Breeds and suggestions for more accessories and items! This really excited us as it proved that there are many more people like us that share our Passion!</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="73" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">Our Company works only with the finest materials &amp; fabrics available to us. Our items are designed with quality &amp; functionality in mind.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">Please feel free to inquire about personalizing with your own Logos or purchasing an exclusive design illustrating your own dog, to use on our available customizables.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">We also offer special pricing on promotionals &amp; Prizes for Kennel Club Events &amp; Shows. As well as customized covers for judging tables or Podium covers with Kennel Club Logos.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator style="double"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="3/12"][vc_single_image image="81" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="9/12"][vc_custom_heading text="OWNER &amp; CREATIVE DESIGNER" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:center|color:%23444444" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;"><strong>Ximena Barrera</strong>, has always been involved in the World of Design and Fashion. Starting her own Jewelry Brand in Central America in 2003.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">She has been involved in the Dog Show World ever since she was a young Girl. She started out Showing her Australian Shepherd Dog "Genie" when she was 14 years old, participating as a Junior Handler and ever since fell in Love with the Breed and with the fascinating World of Show Dogs.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">It became not only her Hobby, but her Passion. She has traveled to many International Dog Shows &amp; Specialties around the World, and enjoys every second of it!</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">In 2013 She had the idea to combine her Passion for Fashion with Dog Shows. Her vision was to create a Company that would cater to the Dog Show clientele.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">She wanted to build a Brand that would somehow break the mold of the traditional &amp; present a new &amp; fresh approach to Dog Show accessories and products. Placing special focus on the personalizing aspect to make each item your own.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator style="double"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="9/12"][vc_custom_heading text="EXECUTIVE MANAGER!" font_container="tag:h4|text_align:center|color:%23444444" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;"><strong>Claudia Cuéllar</strong>, started designing at a very young age on her family business, majored in Marketing &amp; Graphic Design, starting her personal business as a freelance designer in 2010.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">She has been surrounded by dogs her whole life and started breeding American Cocker Spaniels in 2010, the Dog Show World has captivated her heart and this became her new obsession.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">Has worked for several companies around the world in Web design and Product development . In BluNova Collection she got to combine her two passions in life, graphic design &amp; Dogs.</p>\n<p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px;">A self determined creative thinker with an eye for innovation, technical ability and boundless enthusiasm for love, life, design &amp; dogs.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="3/12"][vc_single_image image="83" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'ABOUT US', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '67-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-26 22:28:55', '2015-11-26 22:28:55', '', 67, 'http://localhost/Blu-Nova/?p=80', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
